<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>tail -n 5 seasonal/winter.csv &gt; /home/repl/last.csv : 저장히는방법

tail -n 2 seasonal/winter.csv &gt; bottom.csv
</code></pre></div></div>

