<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cut</span> <span class="nt">-d</span> , <span class="nt">-f</span> 2 seasonal/winter.csv | <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="nt">-v</span> Tooth | <span class="nb">sort</span> <span class="nt">-r</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cut</span> <span class="nt">-d</span>, <span class="nt">-f</span> 2 seasonal/winter.csv | <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="nt">-v</span> Tooth | <span class="nb">sort</span> | <span class="nb">uniq</span> <span class="nt">-c</span> : 중복제거
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl + c </code> : 실행중인 명령 중지</p>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">wc</span> - l seasonal/<span class="k">*</span>.csv | <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="nt">-v</span> total | <span class="nb">sort</span> <span class="nt">-n</span> | <span class="nb">head</span> <span class="nt">-n</span> 1
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="batch-processing">Batch processing</h2>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$OSTYPE</span>

linux-gnu
